                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230625-106-off614 t18230625-106-cd615"></join>, a bag, value 3 d.; a yard of gingham, value 2 s.; a handkerchief, value 6 d.; one half crown, three shillings, and two sixpences the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18230625-106-victim949" type="victimName">
